abstract: The author of “The Glass Castle” and, most recently, “The Silver Star,” is not a fan of “escapist” literature: “Reality is just so interesting, why would you want to escape it?”

abstract: The annual conference for Apple developers started today with a new version of the iOS mobile operating system and a new, streaming music service.
snippet: The annual conference for Apple developers started today with a new version of the iOS mobile operating system and a new, streaming music service.
lead_paragraph: SAN FRANCISCO — As expected, Apple shared details of the next version of its iOS mobile operating system during the opening keynote address at its annual developer conference.

snippet: The choice of Susan E. Rice to replace Tom Donilon as national security adviser represented a defiant gesture to Republicans. Samantha Power was named as the United Nations ambassador.

abstract: James Marsh’s “Shadow Dancer” is the latest film to explore the I.R.A. and Ireland’s turmoil during British occupation.
snippet: James Marsh’s “Shadow Dancer” is the latest film to explore the I.R.A. and Ireland’s turmoil during British occupation.
lead_paragraph: In the grim opening to James Marsh’s “Shadow Dancer,” a girl in Belfast sends her kid brother out on an errand and smack into the turmoil of British occupation in 1973. Cut 20 years later to the girl, now a young woman, riding the London Underground, destination unknown. Until, that is, her strange behavior reveals a new calling as an I.R.A. soldier.

abstract: As Election Day nears in Massachusetts, the race between Gabriel Gomez and Representative Edward J. Markey for the Senate seat vacated by John Kerry has focused on lesser issues.
snippet: As Election Day nears in Massachusetts, the race between Gabriel Gomez and Representative Edward J. Markey for the Senate seat vacated by John Kerry has focused on lesser issues.
lead_paragraph: BOSTON — For an election that was supposed to be about the big issues of the day, the special election in Massachusetts to fill the Senate seat vacated by John Kerry seems to be about everything but.

abstract: Two more teams hit the water for the first time since the death of the sailor Andrew Simpson on May 9 and a day after a review committee outlined new safety suggestions.
snippet: Two more teams hit the water for the first time since the death of the sailor Andrew Simpson on May 9 and a day after a review committee outlined new safety suggestions.
lead_paragraph: The America’s Cup returned to something closer to normal on Thursday as two more of the teams involved in sailing’s premier competition hit the water for the first time since the death of the sailor Andrew Simpson in a training accident on May 9.
